attributes.review: As someone who is a very big supporter of Donald’s, I downloaded the app to support my favorite businessman and president! But the second I opened the app it started asking insanely personal questions, like my home address, names of my relatives, just stuff that isn’t necessary. Hesitant, I filled it in just because I wasn’t going to let that take away my patriotism! Although, after I got through all that chaos it asked me to pay for a monthly subscription! I tried to get around it but it kept bringing me back to the screen, I decided I might as well purchase one month because it was only $18.99 a month. But after I purchased it, I went to look at the app and it barely had three features. Donate to Donald, find Trump rallies near you, and guest services. And the quality was absolute crap! It kept glitching over and over. I was absolutely outraged! This app can’t possibly be by my beloved Don, he would never ask for this of us. Now this app made by who knows has my debit card information, my home address, and my family. I am disgusted and very concerned for my wellbeing and my family’s. I’m absolutely distraught so please, I beg of you, don’t download the app and make the same mistakes I have. It’s not Donald, it’s the Chinese that caused the virus. 🇱🇷🇱🇷🇱🇷
